-- Run this first to see available payment batches
SELECT DISTINCT 
  checkrun_id,
  checkrun_name,
  status_lookup_code,
  bank_account_name,
  check_date
FROM ap_checks_all
WHERE status_lookup_code = 'NEGOTIABLE'
AND UPPER(bank_account_name) LIKE '%SOHAR%'
ORDER BY check_date DESC;
```

This will show you all **NEGOTIABLE** payments from Sohar bank accounts.

